Following code shows how to use GetItemProperty function

// following call gets control under name CustomerName and gets its fore color
Color clr = ItemBindingExtender1.GetItemProperty("CustomerName", "ForeColor");


'following call gets control under name CustomerName and gets its fore color
Dim clr As Color
clr = ItemBindingExtender1.GetItemProperty("CustomerName", "ForeColor")

